## Types of logs [​](https://sapphirejs.dev/docs/Guide/plugins/Logger/getting-started/\#types-of-logs "Direct link to Types of logs")

1. `trace`
2. `debug`
3. `info`
4. `warn`
5. `error`
6. `fatal`

> Example: `container.logger.debug('log debug message');`

